{"tid":394993,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登大軍] 大家一齊去中大學生會fb report個班仆街五毛","createTime":"2017-09-10T12:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T13:19:07.000Z","uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3018084400b14d3bde987406ee7c8d64cc079d98","tid":394993,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:26:13.000Z","msg":"每人report幾十個假ac就夠<br />\n記得report 比1星既post同開垃圾post既五毛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/CUHK.SU/reviews/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FCUHK.SU%2Freviews%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=pHA8xSnmiKajWaFOQZ69K2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=697a6d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/CUHK.SU/reviews/?ref=page_internal</a><br />\n<br />\n支那人憑咩學人上美帝fb呀，仲要係香港人地頭做埋啲咁小學雞既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那留學生咁唔滿意咪唔好黎香港讀書囉，死返大陸飲奶啦屌你仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那人同五毛我屌你老母呀，滾出香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就report左十幾個，雖然班支那人既行為好幼稚，對方人多但咁唔代表佢地有權係香港人既地頭搞事，大家report 得幾多就幾多，積少成多總有啲用既，好過乜都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/202355_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F202355_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d2cbab4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/202359_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F202359_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e90f7944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/202403_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5